==Definition==

<b>hemisphere</b> (<i>noun</i>), plural <b>hemispheres</b>
# (<i>geometry</i>) A half-[[sphere]], formed by a [[plane]] intersecting the center of a sphere.
# (<i>geography</i>) One of the two halves of the [[earth]], namely the [[northern_hemisphere]] or [[southern_hemisphere]].

